п»ҝ/* О“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГү
   LAYOUT О“ГҮГ¶ Navbar, Footer, Page wrappers
   О“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГү */

/* О“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮ NAVBAR О“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮ */

nav {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  z-index: var(--z-nav);
  height: 90px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  padding: 0 4rem;
  background: transparent;
}

/* Floating pill nav on scroll О“ГҮГ¶ like Duck Design */
nav.scrolled {
  height: 64px;
  top: 16px;
  width: 88%;
  max-width: 1080px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: rgba(255, 251, 251, 0.90);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(232, 25, 44, 0.10), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  nav { padding: 0 1.5rem; height: 80px; }
  nav.scrolled { width: 92%; padding: 0 1rem; top: 12px; }
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  nav,
  nav.scrolled {
    top: 0 !important;
    left: 0 !important;
    width: 100% !important;
    max-width: none !important;
    height: 64px !important;
    transform: none !important;
    border-radius: 0 !important;
    padding: 0 1.5rem !important;
    border: 0 !important;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft) !important;
    background: rgba(255,251,251,0.95) !important;
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(232,25,44,0.06) !important;
  }
}

.nav-container-inner {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1440px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  position: relative;
}

/* Logo */
.nav-logo,
.nav-logo-text {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  color: var(--ink);
  text-decoration: none;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 2px;
  z-index: 10;
}
.nav-logo .dot,
.nav-logo strong { color: var(--brand-red); }

/* Center nav links О“ГҮГ¶ pill background like Duck Design */
.nav-center {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.15rem;
  list-style: none;
  padding: 5px;
  background: var(--surface-soft);
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
}
nav.scrolled .nav-center {
  background: transparent;
  border-color: transparent;
}
@media (max-width: 968px) { .nav-center { display: none; } }

.nav-center li { position: relative; }

.nav-center a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 0.55rem 1.15rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  transition: color 0.25s ease;
  display: block;
  z-index: 2;
}
.nav-center a:hover { color: var(--brand-red); }
.nav-center a.active { color: var(--brand-red); font-weight: 700; }

/* Active pill indicator */
.nav-active-pill {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: var(--surface-card);
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  z-index: 1;
}

/* Nav right */
.nav-right {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-md);
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .nav-center, .nav-right .btn-ghost { display: none !important; }
}

/* Mobile layout override for .nav-container-inner */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .nav-container-inner {
    display: grid !important;
    grid-template-columns: 56px minmax(0,1fr) 56px !important;
    align-items: center !important;
    gap: 0.5rem !important;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    grid-column: 2 !important;
    justify-self: center !important;
    position: static !important;
    transform: none !important;
  }
  .nav-right {
    display: contents !important;
  }
  .nav-right .btn-red {
    grid-column: 3 !important;
    justify-self: end !important;
    padding: 0 0.75rem !important;
    min-height: 36px !important;
    font-size: 0.78rem !important;
    border-radius: 8px !important;
  }
  .desktop-cta-label { display: none !important; }
}

/* Mobile hamburger */
.hamburger-btn {
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 5px;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  cursor: none;
  grid-column: 1;
  padding: 0.5rem;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) { .hamburger-btn { display: flex; } }

.hamburger-btn span {
  display: block;
  width: 22px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--ink);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: transform var(--transition-fast), opacity var(--transition-fast);
}
.hamburger-btn.active span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(7px) rotate(45deg); }
.hamburger-btn.active span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
.hamburger-btn.active span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg); }

/* Mobile menu overlay */
.mobile-menu-overlay {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  height: 100dvh;
  background: var(--surface-card);
  z-index: 10005;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
.mobile-menu-inner {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  align-items: center;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
}
.mobile-menu-inner a {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--ink);
  transition: color var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
}
.mobile-menu-inner a:hover {
  color: var(--brand-red);
  transform: translateX(8px);
}
.mobile-menu-footer {
  margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  width: 220px;
}

/* О“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮ Mobile drawer (from Navbar.jsx) О“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮ */
.mobile-menu-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 1.1rem 1.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
}
.mobile-menu-brand {
  display: inline-flex !important;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.55rem;
  color: var(--ink) !important;
  text-decoration: none !important;
}
.mobile-menu-brand img { height: 32px; width: auto; }
.mobile-menu-brand span { color: var(--ink) !important; font-size: 1.38rem !important; font-weight: 900 !important; }
.mobile-menu-brand strong { color: var(--brand-red) !important; font: inherit !important; }
.mobile-menu-head button {
  width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  border: 0; background: transparent; color: var(--muted);
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  cursor: none;
}

.mobile-menu-list {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 0;
  padding: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
}
.mobile-menu-list a {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  min-height: 52px;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  color: var(--ink) !important;
  background: transparent;
  border: 0;
  font-size: 0.96rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast);
}
.mobile-menu-list a + a { border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-soft); }
.mobile-menu-list a.active {
  background: var(--brand-red-soft) !important;
  color: var(--brand-red) !important;
  box-shadow: inset 3px 0 0 var(--brand-red) !important;
}
.mobile-menu-list a svg { color: var(--muted); }

.mobile-search-link {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 22px 1fr auto;
  gap: 0.7rem;
  min-height: 52px;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  background: var(--surface-card);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  color: var(--ink) !important;
  font-size: 0.94rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  align-items: center;
}
.mobile-service-strip {
  display: grid; gap: 0; padding: 0.5rem 0 5rem;
}
.mobile-service-strip a {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  min-height: 46px;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  color: var(--muted) !important;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  align-items: center;
}
.mobile-service-strip a + a { border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-soft); }
.mobile-menu-footer {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  margin-top: auto;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem 1.25rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  background: var(--surface-card);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  align-items: center;
  position: sticky;
  bottom: 0;
}
.mobile-call-link {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink) !important;
  text-decoration: none;
}

/* О“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮ FOOTER О“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮО“Г¶ГҮ */

footer,
footer.footer-v2 {
  background: var(--surface-soft) !important;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft) !important;
  padding: var(--space-xxl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
footer::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--brand-red-soft), transparent);
}

.footer-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.5fr;
  gap: var(--space-xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xxl);
}
@media (max-width: 968px) { .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
@media (max-width: 600px)  { .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); } }

/* Brand */
.footer-brand-mark {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.55rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.footer-brand-mark img { height: 32px; width: auto; }
.footer-brand-mark span { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--ink) !important; }
.footer-brand-mark strong { color: var(--brand-red) !important; font: inherit !important; }

.footer-v2 p,
footer p {
  color: var(--muted) !important;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.65;
  max-width: 280px;
}

/* Social buttons */
.footer-social { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; }
.f-social-btn {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--border-card) !important;
  background: var(--surface-card) !important;
  color: var(--muted) !important;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  transition: all var(--transition-normal);
}
.f-social-btn:hover {
  color: var(--brand-red) !important;
  border-color: var(--brand-red) !important;
  background: var(--brand-red-soft) !important;
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}

/* Footer columns */
.footer-col h4,
.footer-col-title {
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--ink) !important;
  margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
}
.footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.55rem; }
.footer-col ul a,
.footer-col a,
.f-link {
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--muted) !important;
  transition: color var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
  display: inline-block;
}
.footer-col ul a:hover,
.footer-col a:hover,
.f-link:hover {
  color: var(--brand-red) !important;
  transform: translateX(3px);
}

/* Footer contact info */
.footer-contact-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
.f-contact-item small { display: block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.f-contact-item a { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ink) !important; font-weight: 600; }
.f-contact-item a:hover { color: var(--brand-red) !important; }

/* Footer bottom */
.footer-bottom,
.f-bottom {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft) !important;
  padding-top: var(--space-lg);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--space-md);
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--muted) !important;
}
.footer-legal-links,
.f-legal { display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); }
.footer-legal-links a,
.f-legal a {
  color: var(--muted) !important;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  transition: color var(--transition-fast);
}
.footer-legal-links a:hover,
.f-legal a:hover { color: var(--ink) !important; }

/* Page wrapper */
.page-wrapper-anims {
  min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
}
